<p>This tutorial aims to show how to make a <strong>C# Form</strong> with <strong>rounded corners</strong>, using a very simple method. Itâ€™s not actually our policy as we wonâ€™t use code hereâ€¦</p>

<p><strong>1.</strong> Select a background image for the Form(window) - it must have the Formâ€™s size (if the Form is 300x200, the image must be 300x200 too).</p>

