<p><strong>2.</strong> Use a â€˜specificâ€™ color to cover the corners of the image - so it appears with rounded corners - it can be easily done by drawing a rectangle over the original image. This color will be set as transparent, so it will not show up with the window. For this itâ€™s usually used the <strong>Magenta</strong> (R: 255, G: 0, B: 255) color. I recommend using it for the first time.</p>

